- заменить графику для полимера кальция, чтобы он больше ассоциировался с металлическими изделиями.

=====

12plus mod for Rimworld. Sorry for my English, I compiled this description for multilingual families.

What The Mod Does:

This simple xml mod turns off the most hardcore aspects in order to allow 12+ aged children play Rimworld, without getting psychological trauma. For details, see changelog file.

Parents! Now you shouldn't answer kids' ticklish questions during playing.
Kids! Now you can play RimWorld in one room with parents, and to speak about _everything_ happens in your game. For now, only in Russian version.

Current 12plus mod version 0.5.3beta rev.2021.03.21.

=====

Compatibility:

The aim was to make such mods playable:
modpack http://lttlword.ru/rimworld-minimalism-v1-2
modpack http://lttlword.ru/rimworld-sborka-modov-ot-lalks-i-pal
multiplayer https://rimworldmultiplayer.com/post/20_04_17_royalty/
Humanoid Cats — dianawinters.OrassansLite

If you don't like the mod, just turn it off. Saves will be playable.

Not compatible with "Psychology", "Rational Romance" or any other mods altering RimWorld's romance systems.
For now, not compatible with mods for other races or butchering tables and stoves. But we can do the compatibility, just mail to us mailto:uncleshvya@yandex.ru We'll answer as fast as possible.
Not absolutely compatible with auto-script from official Russian translator's site. Basic content is finished, but for guarantied match to "12+" concept, it's better to turn off the auto-updating.

=====

New game:

It's better to start a new game. However, old games are playable too. You should manually delete unwanted traits (see changelog file). There are a lot of video lessons in www, search the string "Rimworld delete trait". Be carefull, delete all 6 unwanted traits from .rws file, and delete old saves.

=====

Known issues:

- if russian "12plus" translation didn't refresh automatically, re-choose russian language in main menu;
- if you open pawn's information panel, and click links too much, it may cause a red error. Just ignore, it's a rare bug;
- if your pawns do not eat, just download another version of erdelf.HumanoidAlienRaces mod;
- sihv.rombones, VanillaExpanded.VCookE and VanillaExpanded.VCookEStews mods were rebalanced during adaptation, see changelog. If you don't like it, just delete "RimOfMadnessBones_Rebalance.xml" or "VEcooking_VEstews_Rebalance.xml" file. Saves will be playable, concept — workable.

